## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not capture the full diversity of immigrant experiences across different demographics and regions. Additionally, the optimism expressed by immigrants may not fully account for the systemic barriers that persist in the U.S. Further research, including longitudinal studies and more diverse narratives, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the immigrant experience in relation to the American Dream.